{
  "message": "fix(wills-share/og): tighten title font to fit on one line\n\nThe 1200x630 OpenGraph variant's title H1 was at fontSize 54 which\ncaused \"Wills & Estate Planning\" to wrap onto two lines (\"Wills &\nEstate\" / \"Planning\"), while the 1200x600 Twitter variant at fontSize\n52 fit cleanly on one line because its illustration column is 20px\nnarrower. Dropping the OG font size to 48 restores a single-line\ntitle that mirrors the Twitter card's rhythm.\n\npublic/og/wills-and-estate-planning-opengraph.jpg regenerated off the\nrebuilt route (91KB JPEG).",
